<TITLE> Prof Rashidul Hasan appointed acting VC to National University </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Dec 26 (bdnews24.com)The education ministry has appointed Prof Sayed Rashidul Hasan as acting VC of the National University, replacing Prof Wakil Ahmed. Rashidul Hasan told bdnews24.com Wednesday that he had received a letter from the ministry, confirming the new appointment. Besides his responsibilities as acting VC, Rashidul Hasan has to work as pro VC and treasurer. He refused to give further details. Prof Wakil Ahmed was appointed during the rule of the four-party coalition government. bdnews
